questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PANKHUDI.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Ministry of Women and Child Development launched the PANKHUDI portal to strengthen CSR and partnership initiatives for women and child welfare.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;PANKHUDI is an integrated digital portal launched by the Ministry of Women and Child Development.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;It aims to streamline CSR contributions and partnerships focused on women and child development.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;The platform brings together NGOs, companies, CSR contributors, NRIs, government agencies and individuals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Portal Features&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt; &lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Registration of contributors and partners&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Submission and tracking of project proposals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Defined approval workflows for transparency&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Supported Missions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Mission Saksham Anganwadi &amp;amp; Poshan 2.0&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Mission Vatsalya&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Mission Shakti&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Operational Framework&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;All contributions processed through non-cash modes&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Ensures traceability, accountability and transparency&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Promotes Jan Bhagidari in governance&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Expected Impact&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Benefits over 14 lakh Anganwadi Centres&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Supports Child Care Institutions, One Stop Centres and Shakti Sadan&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

questions.statement:
&lt;p&gt;Consider the following pairs regarding the &amp;#39;Bhavya Bharat Bhushan&amp;#39; awardees 2026 and their fields:&lt;br /&gt;
I. Dr. Nambi Narayanan &amp;ndash; Science &amp;amp; Technology&lt;br /&gt;
II. Saina Nehwal &amp;ndash; Sports&lt;br /&gt;
III. Dr. Vikram Sampath &amp;ndash; Art and Culture&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Which of the pairs given above are correctly matched?&lt;/p&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;I and II only.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sadhguru&lt;/strong&gt; and Isha Outreach launched the &lt;strong&gt;Bhavya Bharat Bhushan&lt;/strong&gt; awards to honor individuals contributing to India&amp;#39;s growth.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pair I is correct:&lt;/strong&gt; Dr. Nambi Narayanan was honored for his resilience and scientific mastery in rocketry.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pair II is correct:&lt;/strong&gt; Saina Nehwal was recognized for establishing India as a formidable force in global badminton.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pair III is incorrect:&lt;/strong&gt; Dr. Vikram Sampath was honored in Literature and Academcs field&amp;nbsp;for bringing fresh understanding to Bharat&amp;#39;s cultural and political evolution through his research.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The incorrect option&amp;nbsp;is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Infrastructure Risk Guarantee Fund proposed in the Budget will provide full sovereign guarantees to private developers for all phases of infrastructure projects.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Union Finance Minister Nirmala Sitharaman announced a public capital expenditure of ₹12.2 lakh crore in the Union Budget 2026&amp;ndash;27 to accelerate infrastructure-led economic growth.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Public capital expenditure for 2026&amp;ndash;27 has been proposed at ₹12.2 lakh crore, underscoring the government&amp;rsquo;s focus on infrastructure-led growth.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Public capex has risen sharply from ₹2 lakh crore in 2014&amp;ndash;15 to ₹11.2 lakh crore in the Budget Estimates for 2025&amp;ndash;26.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Infrastructure Risk Guarantee Fund will provide prudently calibrated partial credit guarantees to lenders, not full sovereign guarantees.&lt;/strong&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Hence, &lt;strong&gt;Option 3 is incorrect.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The Coastal Cargo Promotion Scheme aims to increase the share of inland waterways and coastal shipping from six per cent to 12 per cent by 2047.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Public Capital Expenditure&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Refers to government spending on long-term assets such as roads, railways, ports, and power infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;It plays a crucial role in crowding in private investment and boosting economic productivity.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Infrastructure Risk Guarantee Fund&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;A proposed mechanism to enhance private sector participation in infrastructure projects.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;It offers partial credit guarantees to lenders during construction and development phases.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Coastal Cargo Promotion Scheme&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Introduced to encourage a modal shift from road and rail to waterways.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Aims to improve logistics efficiency and reduce carbon emissions.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Inland Waterways and Coastal Shipping&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Considered energy-efficient and environmentally sustainable modes of transport.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The Budget targets a significant increase in their share in India&amp;rsquo;s freight movement by 2047.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Knight of the Order of Arts and Letters.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;British fashion designer Victoria Beckham was decorated as a Knight of the Order of Arts and Letters by the French Ministry of Culture in Paris.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Victoria Beckham received the honour during Paris Couture Week at a ceremony held in Paris.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The award was conferred by France&amp;rsquo;s Minister of Culture, Rachida Dati.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The honour recognises Beckham&amp;rsquo;s significant contribution to fashion and the arts.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;She has been showcasing her collections at Paris Fashion Week since 2022.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Order of Arts and Letters&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Established in 1957 by the French government&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Recognises significant contributions to arts, literature and cultural influence in France&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Victoria Beckham&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Former member of the Spice Girls who transitioned into fashion design&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Launched her fashion brand in 2008 and beauty line in 2019&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Notable Recipients&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Demna&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Iris Van Herpen&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Giambattista Valli&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Simon Porte Jacquemus&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

The correct answer is $1 Trillion.
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/in_news.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;In News&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;During the 10th Foundation Day celebrations in New Delhi, the ISA&amp;#39;s role in mobilizing global clean energy finance was highlighted.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Financial Target:&lt;/strong&gt; One of the core missions of the International Solar Alliance (ISA)&amp;nbsp;is to mobilize &lt;strong&gt;$1 trillion&lt;/strong&gt; (USD 1,000 billion) in solar investments by 2030.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Focus Areas:&lt;/strong&gt; The alliance focuses on reducing the cost of technology and financing to support energy-starved regions in &lt;strong&gt;Africa, Asia, and Latin America&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pillars:&lt;/strong&gt; To achieve this, ISA utilizes its &lt;strong&gt;Catalytic Finance Hub&lt;/strong&gt; to mitigate investment risks and attract private capital.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Global Reach:&lt;/strong&gt; With over 120 signatory countries, the ISA is working toward a unified global solar market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); &quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Global Solar Facility&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;This is a financial mechanism under ISA designed to provide payment guarantees and insurance to solar projects, particularly in underdeveloped markets.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;About ISA&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;ISA &lt;/strong&gt;is a collaborative initiative between &lt;strong&gt;India &lt;/strong&gt;and &lt;strong&gt;France&lt;/strong&gt;, conceptualized during &lt;strong&gt;COP21 &lt;/strong&gt;in Paris in &lt;strong&gt;2015&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Following a 2020 amendment to its Framework Agreement, all UN member states are eligible to join the Alliance.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The coalition now includes over 120 countries, with more than 100 signatories and over 90 ratified full members.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Jhansi.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In&lt;strong&gt; Uttar Pradesh&lt;/strong&gt;, the &lt;strong&gt;highest yield of groundnut is in Bundelkhand.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Due to the red soil in&lt;strong&gt; Bundelkhand,&lt;/strong&gt; it is&lt;strong&gt; beneficial for the groundnut crop&lt;/strong&gt;​&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;​The maximum production of litchi&lt;/strong&gt; in the state is done in &lt;strong&gt;Saharanpur and Meerut.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Most oranges &lt;/strong&gt;are produced in the &lt;strong&gt;Saharanpur district of Uttar Pradesh.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Amla&lt;/strong&gt; is grown the most in the state in &lt;strong&gt;Pratapgarh and Allahabad.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The highest production of guava occurs in Shahjahanpur, and Farrukhabad districts respectively.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Barabanki &lt;/strong&gt;is at the fore in &lt;strong&gt;opium production.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sugarcane.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Muzaffarnagar&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;It is a city in&amp;nbsp;Uttar Pradesh.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;It is famous for its sugar industry, paper mills and steel rolling mills.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;According to historians, it was&lt;strong&gt; known as Sarwat in the pre-Mughal era&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;It was gifted by Mughal emperor Shah Jahan to one of his chieftains Muzaffar Khan. Later, the city got renamed &amp;quot;Muzaffarnagar&amp;quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The city is &lt;strong&gt;located in the middle of the highly fertile upper Ganga-Yamuna Doab region.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Important industries in the city&lt;strong&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Sugar and jaggery production.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The state of&lt;strong&gt; Uttar Pradesh is referred to as the sugar bowl of India&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Uttar Pradesh ranks the highest position in the production of the sugar cane crop.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Climatic features&amp;nbsp;for the growth of Sugarcane:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;A long frost-free growing season.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Hot and moist climate.&lt;/li&gt;
