&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Mid-day meal Scheme&amp;#39; was first introduced in 1956 by Tamil Nadu&amp;#39;s Chief Minister K. Kamaraj&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;

